Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your favorite local bowling alley. My name is Alex. How may I assist you today?

Hi Alex, I'm calling about a billing issue I noticed on my statement.

Of course, I’d be happy to help you with that. Could I start by getting your name, please?

Sure, my name is Jamie Brown.

Thank you, Jamie. Could I please have the last four digits of your account number to verify your identity?

It’s one two three four.

Perfect, thank you. And just to confirm, could I have your billing zip code?

It's zero two six six eight.

Great, thank you for that information, Jamie. I'll look into your account now. Just a moment, please.

I’ve found the issue and corrected it on our end. You should see the adjustment on your next billing cycle. Is there anything else I can help you with today?

No, that covers it. Thank you for your help, Alex.

You’re welcome, Jamie. Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Have a wonderful day!
